882
00:41:37,600 --> 00:41:39,440
 znači to je za pet godina,

883
00:41:39,440 --> 00:41:42,340
 Kina dvostroko preteći

884
00:41:42,340 --> 00:41:43,560
 gospodarskom smislu

885
00:41:43,560 --> 00:41:44,780
 sve njamečke države.

886
00:41:45,020 --> 00:41:46,000
 smo se sad razumijeli,

887
00:41:46,000 --> 00:41:47,660
 da je to glavni protivnik.

888
00:41:48,680 --> 00:41:49,700
 A Kina,

889
00:41:49,700 --> 00:41:50,740
 svjesne,

890
00:41:50,740 --> 00:41:53,960
 ruski i kineski stratezi.

891
00:41:53,960 --> 00:41:56,020
 I zato se oni držaju sada zajedno.

892
00:41:56,020 --> 00:41:57,860
 Kao što sam rekao,

893
00:41:57,860 --> 00:41:59,020
 Kina će,

894
00:41:59,020 --> 00:42:00,320
 2000,

895
00:42:00,320 --> 00:42:01,420
 tako su projekcije.

896
00:42:01,420 --> 00:42:03,800
 2030. godine,

897
00:42:03,800 --> 00:42:04,280
 da osjeći,

898
00:42:04,280 --> 00:42:06,600
 mi ti dvostroko imati veću gospodarsku moću

899
00:42:06,600 --> 00:42:07,820
 od Sjednje njamečke države.

900
00:42:07,820 --> 00:42:11,080
 I to je razlog zašto ova preporuka,

901
00:42:11,080 --> 00:42:12,960
 ove dvojice umnijih ljudi je,

902
00:42:12,960 --> 00:42:16,180
 da se ona treba svesti na neku normalnu velesilu.

903
00:42:16,180 --> 00:42:17,600
 Dakle, bit će taj tabor

904
00:42:17,600 --> 00:42:19,020
 kojem ga sada davno zapisao

905
00:42:19,020 --> 00:42:19,740
 u svojom knjigama,

906
00:42:19,740 --> 00:42:21,080
 bit će američki tabor,

907
00:42:21,080 --> 00:42:22,280
 ruski tabor

908
00:42:22,280 --> 00:42:24,380
 i kineski tabor,

909
00:42:24,380 --> 00:42:25,080
 kao ta tvi,

910
00:42:25,080 --> 00:42:26,560
 između njih će postojati

911
00:42:26,560 --> 00:42:28,180
 ti odnosi geopolitike

912
00:42:28,180 --> 00:42:30,020
 na kugli Zamanjsku,

913
00:42:30,020 --> 00:42:32,240
 a ostali su sad sve ispod doli.

914
00:42:32,240 --> 00:42:34,680
 Dakle, trodjelna dioba moći?

915
00:42:34,680 --> 00:42:36,840
 Na najviše strateškoj razini, da.

916
00:42:36,840 --> 00:42:38,700
 I to će biti,

917
00:42:38,700 --> 00:42:39,840
 naravno da će oni u tome,

918
00:42:39,840 --> 00:42:41,840
 tabori svi kod tabori,

919
00:42:41,840 --> 00:42:43,720
 uvijek ima rubni dodiri.

920
00:42:43,720 --> 00:42:44,960
 I tu će biti,

921
00:42:44,960 --> 00:42:46,960
 to je ta determinirani kaos

922
00:42:46,960 --> 00:42:48,600
 koji sam ja prije 20 godina

923
00:42:48,600 --> 00:42:49,560
 napisao u ovom knjizi,

924
00:42:49,560 --> 00:42:51,080
 to je taj Rimljan,

925
00:42:51,080 --> 00:42:52,720
 to su ta tri vrata Euroazije

926
00:42:52,720 --> 00:42:54,140
 gdje se dodiruju oni

927
00:42:54,140 --> 00:42:56,380
 i gdje će moraju biti definirani,

928
00:42:56,380 --> 00:42:57,780
 pa će biti 30 godina

929
00:42:57,780 --> 00:43:00,340
 ti procesi izloženi.

930
00:43:00,340 --> 00:43:02,520
 Hrvatska ima tu jednu prednost,

931
00:43:02,520 --> 00:43:04,640
 veliku, veliku, veliku prednost,

932
00:43:04,640 --> 00:43:08,000
 jer je ona isto dobno

933
00:43:08,000 --> 00:43:13,120
 srednjoevropska i mediteranska sredozemna zemlja.

934
00:43:13,120 --> 00:43:14,660
 Nijedna druge nemaju Europe.

935
00:43:14,660 --> 00:43:16,680
 Na tom prostoru,

936
00:43:16,680 --> 00:43:19,600
 te četvrte graditacijske stočke Evrope,

937
00:43:19,600 --> 00:43:20,960
 u strateškom smislu,

938
00:43:20,960 --> 00:43:24,920
 su sve te tri elipse moći,

939
00:43:24,920 --> 00:43:25,800
 ova tri tabora,

940
00:43:25,800 --> 00:43:26,660
 se presjecaju.

941
00:43:26,660 --> 00:43:27,560
 To je već,

942
00:43:27,560 --> 00:43:28,820
 idemo u teoriju skupova.

943
00:43:28,820 --> 00:43:31,760
 Dakle, presjecište tri skupaje kod nas.

944
00:43:31,760 --> 00:43:34,660
 To je atlantizam ili geopolitika,

945
00:43:34,660 --> 00:43:36,640
 ali sa sonaca toši i amerikanaca.

946
00:43:36,640 --> 00:43:39,200
 Tu je kontinimalizam Rusije

947
00:43:39,200 --> 00:43:41,360
 i njihove geopolitike.

948
00:43:41,360 --> 00:43:43,520
 I to je kineske geopolitike,

949
00:43:43,520 --> 00:43:45,640
 teolokracije ili Novog puta svile.

950
00:43:45,640 --> 00:43:47,700
 Dakle, naša politika,

951
00:43:47,700 --> 00:43:49,260
 da je razumna,

952
00:43:49,260 --> 00:43:50,660
 trebala je voditi politiku

953
00:43:50,660 --> 00:43:53,740
 koju je imao Dubrovačka republika.

954
00:43:53,740 --> 00:43:56,240
 I ona je bila na rastestu

955
00:43:56,240 --> 00:43:58,120
 ondašnjih velesila

956
00:43:58,120 --> 00:44:01,140
 i svidio kako je 600 godina

957
00:44:01,140 --> 00:44:03,640
 opstala i toliko podarila

958
00:44:03,640 --> 00:44:05,580
 ne samo nama Hrvatima,

959
00:44:05,580 --> 00:44:06,660
 u svakome smislu

960
00:44:06,660 --> 00:44:08,120
 od državotvorstva,

961
00:44:08,120 --> 00:44:09,020
 upravljanja,

962
00:44:09,020 --> 00:44:12,080
 gospodarske moći itd.

963
00:44:12,080 --> 00:44:14,380
 Iako nije imala silu,

964
00:44:14,380 --> 00:44:15,540
 ali je imala mudrost.

965
00:44:15,540 --> 00:44:17,900
 Vidite kako se to sve može igrati.

966
00:44:17,900 --> 00:44:21,360
 Ako se ti osvijestiš ono sve,

967
00:44:21,360 --> 00:44:23,000
 osvijestiš svoj identitet.

968
00:44:23,000 --> 00:44:25,980
 Ko je naš verbi problem?

969
00:44:25,980 --> 00:44:27,980
 Što mi nismo osvijestili svoj identitet.

970
00:44:27,980 --> 00:44:29,960
 I zato sam ja napisao knjigu

971
00:44:29,960 --> 00:44:31,200
 uzvišena civilizacija.

972
00:44:31,200 --> 00:44:32,960
 Jer naš intet je uništen

973
00:44:32,960 --> 00:44:34,400
 onoga trenutka kada nije

974
00:44:34,400 --> 00:44:35,780
 okultna oligarhija,

975
00:44:35,780 --> 00:44:37,660
 germanska, njemačka,

976
00:44:37,660 --> 00:44:38,240
 točnije,

977
00:44:38,240 --> 00:44:39,380
 Hasbugovci,

978
00:44:39,380 --> 00:44:41,840
 uvalili nekakve nepostojeće

979
00:44:41,840 --> 00:44:42,380
 slovene

980
00:44:42,380 --> 00:44:43,460
 da se doseli

981
00:44:43,460 --> 00:44:44,580
 u nekakvom 6.

982
00:44:44,580 --> 00:44:45,720
 7. stoljeću.

983
00:44:45,720 --> 00:44:47,500
 A to je znanost dokazala

984
00:44:47,500 --> 00:44:48,840
 da nikakvi veliki seoba

985
00:44:48,840 --> 00:44:49,760
 nije tamo bile.

986
00:44:49,760 --> 00:44:50,420
 Dakle, mi moramo

987
00:44:50,420 --> 00:44:51,560
 prvo svijesti naš intet.

988
00:44:51,560 --> 00:44:52,780
 Zato sam ja napisao tu knjigu.

989
00:44:52,780 --> 00:44:53,900
 Dakle,

990
00:44:53,900 --> 00:44:55,480
 sada su vremena,

991
00:44:55,480 --> 00:44:57,780
 sasvim imamo mogućnosti,

992
00:44:57,840 --> 00:44:59,160
 ješte tu svjećište.

993
00:44:59,160 --> 00:45:00,940
 I naša razumna politika

994
00:45:00,940 --> 00:45:02,120
 ne možemo mi mijenjati.

995
00:45:02,120 --> 00:45:03,040
 Mi moramo uzeti

996
00:45:03,040 --> 00:45:04,080
 datost koja je.

997
00:45:04,080 --> 00:45:05,240
 A datost je

998
00:45:05,240 --> 00:45:06,080
 da smo mi u NATO

999
00:45:06,080 --> 00:45:06,720
 i da smo mi

1000
00:45:06,720 --> 00:45:08,080
 članice EU.

1001
00:45:08,080 --> 00:45:10,640
 Ali vremena će pokazati

1002
00:45:10,640 --> 00:45:11,680
 ništa nije vječno

1003
00:45:11,680 --> 00:45:12,800
 i da će se i NATO

1004
00:45:12,800 --> 00:45:14,240
 i EU raspasti.

1005
00:45:14,240 --> 00:45:14,860
 A što onda?

1006
00:45:15,020 --> 00:45:15,780
 Vjerujete u to?

1007
00:45:15,780 --> 00:45:17,060
 Pa ne, to je uvijek.

1008
00:45:17,060 --> 00:45:17,860
 To je tako.

1009
00:45:17,860 --> 00:45:18,960
 To ne bih kao...

1010
00:45:18,960 --> 00:45:21,160
 Ja vjerujem na onoga razapeta,

1011
00:45:21,160 --> 00:45:22,320
 u Golgosko pobjednika.

1012
00:45:22,320 --> 00:45:23,220
 Ja u toga vjerujem.

1013
00:45:23,220 --> 00:45:25,760
 Ovdje, ja govorim kao strateg.

1014
00:45:25,760 --> 00:45:26,900
 Ako ćemo poći

1015
00:45:26,900 --> 00:45:28,580
 od te mudrosti životna,

1016
00:45:28,580 --> 00:45:30,200
 da ništa nije vječno

1017
00:45:30,200 --> 00:45:32,580
 i da ima svoje rađanje,

1018
00:45:32,580 --> 00:45:33,580
 svoje rast

1019
00:45:33,580 --> 00:45:34,580
 i svoje umiranje.

1020
00:45:34,580 --> 00:45:35,340
 E tako i to.

1021
00:45:35,340 --> 00:45:37,280
 On je nastao,

1022
00:45:37,280 --> 00:45:38,600
 NATO je nastao

1023
00:45:38,600 --> 00:45:40,020
 nakon drugosvjetskog rata

1024
00:45:40,020 --> 00:45:43,240
 i uspostave bipolarne podjele svijeta.

1025
00:45:43,240 --> 00:45:44,560
 Koliko je meni jasno,

1026
00:45:44,560 --> 00:45:46,260
 već koliko 30 godina

1027
00:45:46,260 --> 00:45:48,220
 bipolarne podjele svijeta nema.

1028
00:45:48,220 --> 00:45:50,060
 Ali NATO još ima.

1029
00:45:50,060 --> 00:45:52,960
 A sada ima jednopolarni svijet.

1030
00:45:52,960 --> 00:45:54,380
 On se sada ruši.

1031
00:45:54,380 --> 00:45:56,360
 Prema tome nastaje

1032
00:45:56,360 --> 00:45:58,060
 višepolarnost svijeta,

1033
00:45:58,060 --> 00:46:00,020
 a u višepolarnosti svijeta

1034
00:46:00,020 --> 00:46:01,980
 postavaju ono što je bilo preko

1035
00:46:01,980 --> 00:46:03,620
 prije mora nestati.

1036
00:46:03,620 --> 00:46:05,520
 Jer se će sve transformirati.

1037
00:46:05,520 --> 00:46:08,300
 Admirale, da vas pitam sad.

1038
00:46:08,300 --> 00:46:09,580
 Kad ste malo prije spomenuli

1039
00:46:09,580 --> 00:46:10,340
 Vis Baden.

1040
00:46:10,340 --> 00:46:12,000
 Oko toga se koplja lome

1041
00:46:12,000 --> 00:46:14,120
 i to je jedno popularno odredište

1042
00:46:14,120 --> 00:46:16,300
 za hrvatske političare

1043
00:46:16,300 --> 00:46:17,660
 koji vole reći

1044
00:46:17,660 --> 00:46:18,800
 da tamo nam je mjesto

1045
00:46:18,800 --> 00:46:21,000
 ili ne tamo našim vojnicima nije mjesto.

1046
00:46:21,000 --> 00:46:23,500
 Koliko je po vama moguće

1047
00:46:23,500 --> 00:46:26,200
 da se razvije na evropskom tlu

1048
00:46:26,200 --> 00:46:28,120
 dvostruka linija zapovjedenja

1049
00:46:28,120 --> 00:46:29,780
 vezana uz Rusko?

1050
00:46:29,780 --> 00:46:30,700
 Ovako.

1051
00:46:30,700 --> 00:46:32,100
 Inače, kad govorimo

1052
00:46:32,100 --> 00:46:33,900
 o dvostrukoj liniji zapovjedenja,

1053
00:46:33,900 --> 00:46:35,480
 odnosno, Hrvati bi rekli

1054
00:46:35,480 --> 00:46:37,400
 crti, iako je linija istoj Hrvatskoj.

1055
00:46:37,480 --> 00:46:39,960
 srta nije malo šale, moramo i mi razmeti

1056
00:46:39,960 --> 00:46:41,400
 ovaj ovako.

1057
00:46:41,400 --> 00:46:44,040
 Pa neće da slada ovi sada jezičari

1058
00:46:44,040 --> 00:46:44,860
 jer zbog toga...

1059
00:46:44,860 --> 00:46:46,600
 Možemo neko rade što god hoće,

1060
00:46:46,600 --> 00:46:48,140
 jer moramo mi gajiti

1061
00:46:48,140 --> 00:46:50,020
 naš Hrvatski prekrasni jezik

1062
00:46:50,020 --> 00:46:50,720
 i tako dalje.

1063
00:46:51,680 --> 00:46:53,940
 sve uzeti druge i dobro je linija,

1064
00:46:53,940 --> 00:46:56,080
 jer ima negdje gdje možeš uporaviti crto,

1065
00:46:56,080 --> 00:46:58,240
 ali ne možeš uporaviti...

1066
00:46:58,240 --> 00:46:59,900
 bolje uporaviti liniju.

1067
00:46:59,900 --> 00:47:01,880
 Evo, pa sve je to u redu,

1068
00:47:01,880 --> 00:47:03,140
 jedno i drugo je dobro došlo.

1069
00:47:03,140 --> 00:47:05,880
 Dakle, ne spijemo biti s tim uptereseni.

1070
00:47:05,880 --> 00:47:07,300
 Ništa, bogatstvo Hrvatskog jezika

1071
00:47:07,300 --> 00:47:07,940
 iznad svega.

1072
00:47:07,940 --> 00:47:08,840
 Tako je, tako je.

1073
00:47:08,840 --> 00:47:11,620
 Bogatstvo, stvarno je Hrvatski jezik

1074
00:47:11,620 --> 00:47:13,700
 bogat u mnogim elementima.

1075
00:47:13,700 --> 00:47:17,140
 Idemo sada na ovo pitanje...

1076
00:47:17,960 --> 00:47:19,700
 Dvostruka crta ili dvostruka linija.

1077
00:47:19,700 --> 00:47:21,380
 Dakle, dvostruka crta je izmišljena

1078
00:47:21,380 --> 00:47:22,480
 samo za nas Hrvate,

1079
00:47:22,480 --> 00:47:24,220
 kao što je izmišljena

1080
00:47:24,220 --> 00:47:26,180
 preko mjerno granatiranje.

1081
00:47:26,180 --> 00:47:27,640
 Ajde sad.

1082
00:47:27,640 --> 00:47:30,060
 Ja zavodio.

1083
00:47:30,060 --> 00:47:32,740
 U našoj operaciji Olujer,

1084
00:47:32,740 --> 00:47:34,480
 u napadu na Knin,

1085
00:47:34,480 --> 00:47:36,700
 topično-raketne snage

1086
00:47:36,700 --> 00:47:39,900
 gađale su šest ciljeva.

1087
00:47:39,900 --> 00:47:41,320
 Nabranje ih.

1088
00:47:41,320 --> 00:47:43,380
 Jedna vojarna, druga vojarna,

1089
00:47:43,380 --> 00:47:44,360
 treća vojarna,

1090
00:47:44,360 --> 00:47:46,300
 odnosno zgrada,

1091
00:47:46,560 --> 00:47:48,880
 granaštaba vojske srpske krajine,

1092
00:47:48,880 --> 00:47:51,200
 rezultencija predsjednika Martića

1093
00:47:51,200 --> 00:47:52,740
 i glavno Raskriži u Kninu.

1094
00:47:52,740 --> 00:47:55,740
 Dakle, svi šeste su vojni ciljere.

1095
00:47:55,740 --> 00:47:59,460
 Ispaljeno po srskim izvješćima,

1096
00:47:59,460 --> 00:48:00,720
 gdje smo iskilili,

1097
00:48:00,720 --> 00:48:01,900
 ja se ovdje u vojnovojstvu službu,

1098
00:48:01,900 --> 00:48:04,000
 u Beograd i Banja Luku,

1099
00:48:04,000 --> 00:48:08,700
 gdje piše šef vojno-obraštane službe

1100
00:48:08,700 --> 00:48:10,620
 te vojske, te pseudovojske,

1101
00:48:10,620 --> 00:48:12,640
 dakle, nazovimo to uvjetno

1102
00:48:12,640 --> 00:48:14,260
 moj kolega sa druge strane,

1103
00:48:15,160 --> 00:48:16,220
 svom kolegi,

1104
00:48:16,220 --> 00:48:19,980
 načelniku oboještene uprave u Beogradu,

1105
00:48:19,980 --> 00:48:24,080
 da su Hrvati ispalili,

1106
00:48:24,080 --> 00:48:25,360
 sve slušajte,

1107
00:48:25,360 --> 00:48:29,160
 250 do 300 projektila rašto kalibra

1108
00:48:29,160 --> 00:48:31,580
 i da su gađali ovi šest siljeva.

1109
00:48:31,680 --> 00:48:32,940
 To oni su povijek na brojni.

1110
00:48:32,940 --> 00:48:36,260
 I kaže, mora se priznati da su pogodili

1111
00:48:36,260 --> 00:48:39,260
 i ovo generalna štab.

1112
00:48:39,260 --> 00:48:43,880
 Kaže, mora da je tamo neki dobar artiljerac,

1113
00:48:43,880 --> 00:48:46,060
 kad je tako mogao ubaciti to.

1114
00:48:46,320 --> 00:48:49,700
 A to je ubacio, su bile besplote letali sa povijedanje

1115
00:48:49,700 --> 00:48:51,280
 i možeš odmah korekciju da me govori.

1116
00:48:51,280 --> 00:48:56,340
 Notabene, na Hrvatskom sudju se je dokazalo

1117
00:48:56,340 --> 00:48:59,420
 da je samo u Gorjom knjinu,

1118
00:48:59,420 --> 00:49:00,860
 odnosno točnije u Golubiću,

1119
00:49:00,860 --> 00:49:03,360
 nastradao samo jedan civil i to vjerojatno,

1120
00:49:03,360 --> 00:49:04,760
 ne od nikakvog djelovanja,

1121
00:49:04,760 --> 00:49:07,600
 vjerojatno ispao iz ovoga traktora što su oni išli,

1122
00:49:07,600 --> 00:49:08,900
 nešto slično se da godin.

1123
00:49:09,440 --> 00:49:13,720
 I sada usporedite to ovoj što se događa u Gazi

1124
00:49:13,720 --> 00:49:15,840
 ili što se događa u Beirutu, Libanonu.

1125
00:49:15,840 --> 00:49:20,020
 Dakle, izmišljenio je pojem prekomjernog granatiranja

1126
00:49:20,020 --> 00:49:23,080
 da bi se naš general Gotovina i naš general Markač

1127
00:49:23,080 --> 00:49:25,900
 proglasili ratnim zločinicima u Hagu.

1128
00:49:25,900 --> 00:49:26,980
 To je jedan pojem.

1129
00:49:26,980 --> 00:49:29,980
 Onda sad tim ide topniški dnevnice.

1130
00:49:29,980 --> 00:49:34,820
 Nikakva vojska nema topniške dnevnice.

1131
00:49:34,820 --> 00:49:38,260
 E, sad tim je, da bi se to dokazalo,

1132
00:49:38,260 --> 00:49:41,540
 inače to izmislio, tu crtu u slučaju Blaškića,

1133
00:49:41,540 --> 00:49:43,520
 odvjetnik Anton Obilo.

1134
00:49:43,520 --> 00:49:46,780
 Nema vojska dvostruku crtu.

1135
00:49:46,780 --> 00:49:49,040
 Niti može imati jer je to čista kirarkija.

1136
00:49:49,040 --> 00:49:51,820
 Ili imaš crtu ili je nemaš.

1137
00:49:51,820 --> 00:49:56,020
 Zanimljivo je, kod te dvostruke crtve,

1138
00:49:56,020 --> 00:50:00,600
 kod nas Hrvata, ta dvostruka, kriva crta,

1139
00:50:00,600 --> 00:50:03,940
 bili bi ovako predsjednik Tuđva,

1140
00:50:03,940 --> 00:50:07,240
 ministar Šušak, general Bobetkoj, sad mi i ostali.

1141
00:50:07,240 --> 00:50:10,660
 Ali oni, to je po njima kriva crta,

1142
00:50:10,660 --> 00:50:14,560
 ili ta dvostruka, a ta druga koja bi po njima bile prava,

1143
00:50:14,560 --> 00:50:15,880
 nikad nisu definirali.

1144
00:50:15,880 --> 00:50:18,360
 Dakle, nema.

1145
00:50:18,360 --> 00:50:20,520
 U ovome slučaju je, slučaju,

1146
00:50:20,520 --> 00:50:24,200
 vratimo se na ovom Vizbadenu.

1147
00:50:24,200 --> 00:50:26,900
 To je, što je rekao naš predsjednik,

1148
00:50:26,900 --> 00:50:29,020
 Zora Milanović, ispravno.

1149
00:50:29,100 --> 00:50:36,420
 To je operativno za pojedništvo, za izvođenje druge etape rata zapada,

1150
00:50:36,420 --> 00:50:40,800
 u ovome slučaju, Europe protiv Rusije.

1151
00:50:40,800 --> 00:50:47,600
 I sada, u ovo zadnje vrijeme, bilo je zaokupljeno svim novim oružjem,

1152
00:50:48,140 --> 00:50:51,400
 koja je lansirana od strane ruskih snaga,

1153
00:50:51,400 --> 00:50:55,820
 a to je orešnik, ako mi kažemo, ruski ariješnik,

1154
00:50:55,820 --> 00:50:58,860
 na Njepo-Petrovsk.

1155
00:50:58,860 --> 00:51:04,140
 Točnije, na veliki proizvodni kapacitet.

1156
00:51:04,560 --> 00:51:08,160
 Zove se Južmaš, gdje u vrijeme Sovjetskog savjeza

1157
00:51:08,160 --> 00:51:10,220
 se proizvodili, između ostaloga,

1158
00:51:10,220 --> 00:51:13,180
 rekatni motori iza svemirske letove,

1159
00:51:13,180 --> 00:51:14,500
 naravno, iza rakete.

1160
00:51:14,500 --> 00:51:17,680
 Rijepeno, kakve simbolike u tome?

1161
00:51:17,680 --> 00:51:19,760
 Ima, ima, ima velike simbolike.

1162
00:51:19,760 --> 00:51:21,640
 To ljudi ne znaju.

1163
00:51:21,640 --> 00:51:25,180
 Njepo-Petrovsk, sada go oni zovu Dnjipro,

1164
00:51:25,180 --> 00:51:27,360
 kao i rijeku, to je Dnjepro uvijek,

1165
00:51:27,360 --> 00:51:31,460
 mislim, to nekako rade tako kao hoće.

1166
00:51:31,460 --> 00:51:34,060
 A sama riječ govori Dnjepo-Petrovsk,

1167
00:51:34,060 --> 00:51:36,060
 dakle, to je grad Petrov nad Dnjepro.

1168
00:51:36,060 --> 00:51:38,660
 Mislim, govori što je i koga je osnovio,

1169
00:51:38,660 --> 00:51:39,540
 dakle, Petar Veliki.

1170
00:51:39,540 --> 00:51:40,260
 Petar Veliki, da.

1171
00:51:40,260 --> 00:51:42,420
 A zanimljivo z Dnjepo-Petrovska je u to,

1172
00:51:42,420 --> 00:51:45,420
 što se tu nalazi najveća sinagoga na svijetu.

1173
00:51:45,420 --> 00:51:50,620
 Inače, vrlo blizu Dnjepo-Petrovska

1174
00:51:50,620 --> 00:51:54,640
 je bilo Hazarsko glavni grad,

1175
00:51:54,640 --> 00:51:55,940
 nazovemo je, zvao se Itil.

1176
00:51:55,940 --> 00:51:58,680
 Dakle, od 8. do 10. stoljeća

1177
00:51:58,680 --> 00:52:00,380
 tu je bila Hazarska država,

1178
00:52:00,380 --> 00:52:02,880
 Hazarska država na čelu je bio

1179
00:52:03,560 --> 00:52:05,180
 Kagan. Dakle, dalje,

1180
00:52:05,180 --> 00:52:07,560
 odatle se, to su bio

1181
00:52:07,560 --> 00:52:09,380
 turkijski narod koji je doselio

1182
00:52:09,380 --> 00:52:11,680
 na ta područaj i koji je uzeo

1183
00:52:11,680 --> 00:52:13,120
 hebrejsku vjeru.

1184
00:52:13,120 --> 00:52:15,460
 To su ti velika većina

1185
00:52:15,460 --> 00:52:17,700
 današnjih židova ili Hazara.

1186
00:52:17,700 --> 00:52:19,340
 Oni sebe vole zvati

1187
00:52:19,340 --> 00:52:20,160
 Aškenazima.

1188
00:52:20,160 --> 00:52:21,100
 Da su oni potremci.

1189
00:52:21,180 --> 00:52:22,900
 Oni nisu govorili

1190
00:52:22,900 --> 00:52:25,440
 ni hebrejski, ni ti pisali hebrejski pismo.

1191
00:52:25,440 --> 00:52:26,120
 Oni imaju svoje,

1192
00:52:26,120 --> 00:52:28,100
 koje se zove Jidiš.

1193
00:52:28,100 --> 00:52:30,880
 Jidiš može se dobro razumijeti.

1194
00:52:30,880 --> 00:52:33,240
 Onaj ko govori staro-njemaški,

1195
00:52:33,240 --> 00:52:34,520
 staro-germanski, jezki,

1196
00:52:34,520 --> 00:52:37,360
 ima tu puno ovih naših burinskih riječi.

1197
00:52:37,360 --> 00:52:38,600
 Dakle, burini, mi smo potom

1198
00:52:38,600 --> 00:52:40,460
 cilira, ne slaveni, a i zove burini.

1199
00:52:40,460 --> 00:52:42,300
 Dakle, to je to.

1200
00:52:42,460 --> 00:52:43,640
 Moralo se razgovoriti.

1201
00:52:43,640 --> 00:52:45,200
 Ovo što se događa u Ukrajini,

1202
00:52:45,200 --> 00:52:45,960
 to je neki rat.

1203
00:52:45,960 --> 00:52:47,280
 I tu je Hazarsku,

1204
00:52:47,280 --> 00:52:48,000
 tu carstvo,

1205
00:52:48,000 --> 00:52:51,200
 Razorija, jer se oni išli napasti

1206
00:52:51,200 --> 00:52:53,200
 Kijevsku Rusiju.

1207
00:52:53,200 --> 00:52:55,880
 Dakle, to je središte ruskog zala se

1208
00:52:55,880 --> 00:52:56,700
 Kijevska Rusija.

1209
00:52:56,700 --> 00:52:59,640
 I u devetom stoljeću išli se napasti

1210
00:52:59,640 --> 00:53:01,920
 i onda se oni Hazariju pobjedio.

1211
00:53:01,920 --> 00:53:04,580
 Ruski knjez svjatovstvo prvi,

1212
00:53:04,580 --> 00:53:06,440
 a potpuno je rasturio.

1213
00:53:06,440 --> 00:53:07,520
 To je Vladimir Veliki.

1214
00:53:07,520 --> 00:53:09,080
 Zato se on zove Vladimir Veliki.

1215
00:53:09,080 --> 00:53:10,680
 Zato je toliko

1216
00:53:10,680 --> 00:53:14,220
 popularno ime Vladimir

1217
00:53:14,220 --> 00:53:15,740
 kod Rusa.

1218
00:53:15,740 --> 00:53:17,660
 Pa evo, i danas su protagonisti

1219
00:53:17,660 --> 00:53:19,300
 u Ukrajini dvoja Vladimira.

1220
00:53:19,300 --> 00:53:20,900
 Da, pa ćeš nećiš.

1221
00:53:20,900 --> 00:53:22,160
 Sve dođe na vladu.

1222
00:53:22,160 --> 00:53:23,820
 A u Hrvatskoj na šeksa.

1223
00:53:23,820 --> 00:53:24,560
 Molim.

1224
00:53:24,560 --> 00:53:25,780
 A u Hrvatskoj na šeksa.

1225
00:53:25,780 --> 00:53:26,780
 A u Hrvatskoj na šeksa.

1226
00:53:26,780 --> 00:53:27,800
 Kod nas on sve ima.

1227
00:53:27,800 --> 00:53:29,340
 On to radi i oblači.

1228
00:53:29,340 --> 00:53:30,580
 Dakle, to su

1229
00:53:30,580 --> 00:53:32,840
 sada ti događe.

1230
00:53:32,840 --> 00:53:34,320
 Vracimo se ome za pojednišću.

1231
00:53:34,320 --> 00:53:35,160
 Sve to važno.

1232
00:53:35,160 --> 00:53:36,000
 Pravno.

1233
00:53:36,000 --> 00:53:37,980
 I kada je lansiran rešnik,

1234
00:53:38,900 --> 00:53:40,880
 onda je opet, opet.

1235
00:53:40,880 --> 00:53:42,520
 Kod nas ne zove onaj ko zna.

1236
00:53:42,520 --> 00:53:44,400
 Ko zna.

1237
00:53:44,400 --> 00:53:45,920
 Njega ne zove da uprotumači.

1238
00:53:45,920 --> 00:53:47,980
 Recimo, ja sam nakon završetka

1239
00:53:47,980 --> 00:53:48,880
 Vojne akademije,

1240
00:53:48,880 --> 00:53:51,260
 odnosno fakulteta

1241
00:53:51,260 --> 00:53:52,460
 Vojno-Pomorskoga,

1242
00:53:52,460 --> 00:53:54,380
 imao specializaciju

1243
00:53:54,380 --> 00:53:56,040
 između ostaloga

1244
00:53:56,040 --> 00:53:58,700
 borba protipanetnih raketa

1245
00:53:58,700 --> 00:53:59,800
 i borba protipodmorca.

1246
00:54:00,020 --> 00:54:01,740
 govorim od onašeg vremena.

1247
00:54:01,740 --> 00:54:02,520
 Nije to istog.

1248
00:54:02,520 --> 00:54:04,920
 Danas je to normo otišlo.

1249
00:54:04,920 --> 00:54:07,160
 Ali mogu te tragove pratiti.

1250
00:54:07,160 --> 00:54:08,720
 To je jednostavno tako.

1251
00:54:08,720 --> 00:54:09,960
 Kako imate specializaciju,

1252
00:54:09,960 --> 00:54:10,780
 možete vrlo brzo

1253
00:54:10,780 --> 00:54:12,940
 i nove stvari naučiti.

1254
00:54:12,940 --> 00:54:14,360
 Znate što je unutarnja,

1255
00:54:14,360 --> 00:54:16,300
 što je vanjski strategijski krug.

1256
00:54:16,300 --> 00:54:19,120
 I sada ovi ostali,

1257
00:54:19,120 --> 00:54:22,200
 pa onda je to bila raketa

1258
00:54:22,200 --> 00:54:25,040
 RS-27 rubež,

1259
00:54:25,040 --> 00:54:27,400
 rubež je inače granica u ruskom,

1260
00:54:27,400 --> 00:54:28,480
 rubež, rub.

1261
00:54:28,480 --> 00:54:30,740
 To je granica u ruskom jesku.

1262
00:54:30,740 --> 00:54:32,500
 Pa onda je, nije,

1263
00:54:32,500 --> 00:54:33,800
 pa onda ne znamo,

1264
00:54:33,800 --> 00:54:35,360
 rješnik zašto je on,

1265
00:54:35,360 --> 00:54:36,200
 pa je li to.

1266
00:54:36,200 --> 00:54:37,460
 Ovdje jednostavno ovako.

1267
00:54:37,460 --> 00:54:41,180
 Rusi, budući da su dosegli

1268
00:54:41,180 --> 00:54:42,500
 vladanjem

1269
00:54:42,500 --> 00:54:44,020
 hiperzvučne,

1270
00:54:44,020 --> 00:54:45,720
 hipersofnične tehnologije,

1271
00:54:46,300 --> 00:54:49,560
 oni imaju mnoge rakete

1272
00:54:49,560 --> 00:54:51,880
 koje su još iz vremena

1273
00:54:51,880 --> 00:54:52,820
 Sovjetskog savjeza.

1274
00:54:52,820 --> 00:54:54,200
 Neke su napustili,

1275
00:54:54,200 --> 00:54:55,080
 neke poboljšali.

1276
00:54:55,080 --> 00:54:57,400
 I te su rakete nosači,

1277
00:54:57,400 --> 00:54:58,380
 nositelji.

1278
00:54:58,380 --> 00:55:01,960
 I naravno da je ta raketa,

1279
00:55:01,960 --> 00:55:03,960
 recimo Pandan,

1280
00:55:03,960 --> 00:55:05,960
 te rakete RS-26

1281
00:55:05,960 --> 00:55:07,500
 je američki Pershing.

1282
00:55:07,500 --> 00:55:09,180
 To se definira

1283
00:55:09,180 --> 00:55:10,200
 u ovim sporozima

1284
00:55:10,200 --> 00:55:11,360
 o nuklearnom oružju

1285
00:55:11,360 --> 00:55:13,460
 kao rakete srednjeg dometa

1286
00:55:13,460 --> 00:55:14,060
 i jesu.

1287
00:55:14,060 --> 00:55:16,220
 Rakete srednjega dometa

1288
00:55:16,220 --> 00:55:18,980
 su do 5,5 tisuća kilometara.

1289
00:55:18,980 --> 00:55:20,860
 Iznad toga

1290
00:55:20,860 --> 00:55:23,380
 su rakete

1291
00:55:23,380 --> 00:55:24,580
 strateške namjene.

1292
00:55:24,580 --> 00:55:27,700
 Jedne i druge

1293
00:55:27,700 --> 00:55:29,020
 su balističke rakete.

1294
00:55:29,020 --> 00:55:30,300
 Znači, lete je po nekom

1295
00:55:30,300 --> 00:55:31,920
 krivulju ovako otprilike.

1296
00:55:31,920 --> 00:55:34,220
 Recimo, približno nekakva parabola,

1297
00:55:34,220 --> 00:55:35,500
 nije čista parabola,

1298
00:55:35,500 --> 00:55:37,620
 nisu im ovi krakovi isti,

1299
00:55:37,620 --> 00:55:39,260
 ali slišno može.

1300
00:55:39,260 --> 00:55:39,760
 Evo, rako.

1301
00:55:39,760 --> 00:55:41,200
 Evo, pokazujem ruku.

1302
00:55:42,480 --> 00:55:42,840
 sada,

1303
00:55:42,840 --> 00:55:45,060
 ova raketa koja nosi

1304
00:55:45,060 --> 00:55:46,380
 neku bojevu glavu,

1305
00:55:46,380 --> 00:55:47,440
 grećemo bojevom glave,

1306
00:55:47,440 --> 00:55:49,440
 ona, kada se lansira,

1307
00:55:49,440 --> 00:55:51,160
 ona se diže

1308
00:55:51,160 --> 00:55:52,080
 gore,

1309
00:55:52,080 --> 00:55:53,740
 dođe u vršnu točku

1310
00:55:53,740 --> 00:55:55,120
 i ota se spušta

1311
00:55:55,120 --> 00:55:55,820
 prema cilju

1312
00:55:55,820 --> 00:55:56,840
 koji je programiran,

1313
00:55:56,840 --> 00:55:57,420
 taj cilj.

1314
00:55:57,420 --> 00:56:01,320
 Ona, u vršnu točku,

1315
00:56:01,320 --> 00:56:02,740
 završava svoju misiju,

1316
00:56:02,740 --> 00:56:04,400
 tada se otvara

1317
00:56:04,400 --> 00:56:05,580
 ta bojeva glava

1318
00:56:05,580 --> 00:56:07,620
 i iz nje izlaze

1319
00:56:07,620 --> 00:56:09,720
 1, 2, 3, pa 12,

1320
00:56:09,720 --> 00:56:10,540
 u nekim čak

1321
00:56:10,540 --> 00:56:12,400
 može izići i 15

1322
00:56:12,400 --> 00:56:14,420
 modula,

1323
00:56:14,420 --> 00:56:17,840
 odnosno blokova

1324
00:56:17,840 --> 00:56:20,540
 u kojima ima

1325
00:56:20,540 --> 00:56:22,020
 eksploziv ili nešto drugo.

1326
00:56:22,100 --> 00:56:23,080
 smo se sad razumijeli,

1327
00:56:23,080 --> 00:56:25,700
 protiraketni sustavi,

1328
00:56:25,700 --> 00:56:27,600
 najosjetljiviji

1329
00:56:27,600 --> 00:56:29,760
 je od momenta starta

1330
00:56:29,760 --> 00:56:30,980
 do dolazga ove točke

1331
00:56:30,980 --> 00:56:32,680
 i zato se rade

1332
00:56:32,680 --> 00:56:34,140
 protiraketni sustavi,

1333
00:56:34,140 --> 00:56:35,880
 da oni u ovom

1334
00:56:35,880 --> 00:56:36,960
 uzlasnom putanju

1335
00:56:36,960 --> 00:56:38,580
 pogode ove rakete

1336
00:56:38,580 --> 00:56:39,840
 i onda su riješili problem

1337
00:56:39,840 --> 00:56:40,660
 jer neće doći

1338
00:56:40,660 --> 00:56:41,960
 do otvaranja bojeve glave.

1339
00:56:41,960 --> 00:56:43,880
 I to je američki

1340
00:56:43,880 --> 00:56:45,060
 protiraketni štit

1341
00:56:45,060 --> 00:56:47,140
 koji je u Poljskoj

1342
00:56:47,140 --> 00:56:49,560
 i u Rumunjskoj.

1343
00:56:49,560 --> 00:56:50,840
 Zove se A2D.

1344
00:56:51,880 --> 00:56:53,020
 Isto tako i Rusija

1345
00:56:53,020 --> 00:56:54,880
 ima za ove američke rakete.

1346
00:56:54,880 --> 00:56:56,300
 Dakle, jedne i drugi imaju.

1347
00:56:56,300 --> 00:56:58,120
 I sada,

1348
00:56:58,120 --> 00:56:59,360
 kada raketa dođe

1349
00:56:59,360 --> 00:57:00,200
 u tu poziciju,

1350
00:57:00,200 --> 00:57:01,520
 otvori se bojeva glava,

1351
00:57:01,520 --> 00:57:02,800
 u ovom slučaju

1352
00:57:02,800 --> 00:57:03,600
 riješnika

1353
00:57:03,600 --> 00:57:04,620
 ili orešnika,

1354
00:57:04,620 --> 00:57:09,180
 izlaze šest blokova.

1355
00:57:09,180 --> 00:57:11,400
 Ova raketa

1356
00:57:11,400 --> 00:57:11,940
 dosežu

1357
00:57:11,940 --> 00:57:13,600
 hiperzvučnu brzinu,

1358
00:57:13,600 --> 00:57:16,340
 ali i svaka strateška raketa

1359
00:57:16,340 --> 00:57:18,080
 ima hiperzvučnu brzinu.

1360
00:57:18,080 --> 00:57:18,880
 Ali to nije to.

1361
00:57:18,880 --> 00:57:20,160
 Jer ovo ne djeluje.

1362
00:57:20,160 --> 00:57:21,420
 Ove se dignu gore

1363
00:57:21,420 --> 00:57:22,300
 u atmosferu

1364
00:57:22,300 --> 00:57:23,600
 gdje nema otvora zraka.

1365
00:57:23,600 --> 00:57:24,780
 Ali ovo ide gdje je zrak.

1366
00:57:24,780 --> 00:57:27,120
 I zato kada ove rakete

1367
00:57:27,120 --> 00:57:28,580
 iziče ovih šest blokova,

1368
00:57:28,580 --> 00:57:31,080
 tada one postižu brzinu,

1369
00:57:31,080 --> 00:57:31,800
 jer tako oni imaju

1370
00:57:31,800 --> 00:57:32,560
 svoje motore,

1371
00:57:32,560 --> 00:57:35,480
 brzinu od deseti pomaka.

1372
00:57:36,200 --> 00:57:37,120
 I one sad ide

1373
00:57:37,120 --> 00:57:38,320
 o silaznu putanju.

1374
00:57:38,320 --> 00:57:39,720
 Već sada djeluje

1375
00:57:39,720 --> 00:57:40,200
 što?

